milestones.description: Kevin Sandher and Codrington's 31-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 30 between Kevin Sandher and Codrington
This is the lowest match aggregate (366) involving teams Canada & Kenya in ODIs
John Davison has broken the record for most catches (3) in ODIs for CAN, going past Fazil Sattaur's 2
Ashish Bagai has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (9) for CAN, going past John Davison
